cs.IT, cs.AR, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.ET

This paper is about improving the error performance of list decoding algorithms for polar codes, which are commonly used in information theory (cs.IT) and communication systems (cs.AR). The paper also proposes a new architecture for partial sum computation units, which involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and embedded systems (cs.ET). Finally, the paper discusses the overall system design and optimization, which is related to control systems (cs.SY).
